        <h2 class="Bali">Balinese food</h2>
        <p>Actual Balinese food is common on the island but it has made few inroads in the rest of the country due to its emphasis on pork, which is anathema to the largely Muslim population in the rest of the country. Notable dishes include:</p>
        <img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/c/cc/Chicken_satay_on_banana_leaf_in_Java.jpg/411px-Chicken_satay_on_banana_leaf_in_Java.jpg" width="300" id="satay">
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Babi guling</strong></li>
            <li><strong>Bebek betutu</strong></li>
            <li><strong>Lawar</strong></li>
            <li><strong>Satay lilit</strong></li>
            <li><strong>Urutan</strong></li>
